@hailin0 If you are sure that `fall through` is required, you should add the specified comment.

`// fall through`, `// fallthru` and `/* fall-thru */` are all valid, for examples:

```
 switch (i) {
   case 1:
     i++; // fall through
   case 2:
     i++;
     // fallthru
   case 3: {
     i++;
   }
   /* fall-thru */
}
```

